reviewText: One of my all-time favorite musician-songster lineups!
Fantastic video of one of Ireland's great bands.  Nice close up shots of the band members.

One of the best live shows I've seen. Planxty are legendary and we are blessed to have had them get together again for this performance. The quality of the recording and DVD are excellent and the musicianship is outstanding. 5 out of 5!

Excellent! This is a great dvd, the band, the songs, the camerawork are all great.
There are 15 songs plus 3 extra tracks. My favorites were Little Musgrave and As I Roved Out. It's great to have the opportunity to see this band in concert.
